static image and text content for each onboarding slide; it does not request runtime permissions, handle permission callbacks, or access protected platform APIs.\",\n290:         \"`OnBoardingItem.get()` loads the full onboarding data set by returning a fixed ordered list of three slide definitions. The method is the source of onboarding page content and preserves the slide order used by the pager.\",\n291:         \"`OnBoardingItem.get()` returns three resource IDs for onboarding slide artwork, titles, and descriptions. It supplies static drawable references only and does not implement image preview, zoom, or metadata behavior.\",\n292:         \"`OnBoardingItem.get()` is a pure in-memory list factory for onboarding slide resources. It does not request permissions or reach protected APIs.\",\n293:         \"OnBoarding owns the pager navigation surface: tapping the trailing action advances to the next page until the last slide, then navigates to `Screen.LoginScreen.route`.\",\n294:         \"OnBoarding observes pager state through `pagerState.currentPage` so indicator selection and next/final action behavior update immediately as the user swipes or taps next.\",\n295:         \"OnBoarding coordinates pager state, window color styling, and login navigation only; it does not request permissions, process permission results, or use protected APIs.\",\n296:         \"OnBoarding performs route-entry setup by creating coroutine and pager state, loading slide items, and applying onboarding-specific status/navigation bar colors while the onboarding screen is active.\",\n297:         \"BottomSection renders only onboarding indicators and a trailing next button. It does not request permissions or access protected APIs.\",\n298:         \"Indicators and Indicator render animated onboarding progress pills only. They do not request permissions or touch protected APIs.\"\n299:       ],\n300:       \"acceptanceEvidence\": [\n\n(Showing lines 1-300 of 1349. Use offset=301 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"{\n  \"schemaVersion\": 1,\n  \"generatedAt\": \"2026-06-25T11:44:24+00:00\",\n  \"phase\": \"phase-03-onboarding-login-profile\",\n  \"purpose\": \"Phase implementation-group verdicts generated after grouped implementation batches. Use this as a bounded group-repair queue before the normal phase coverage gate.\",\n  \"summary\": {\n    \"implementationGroups\": 4,\n    \"repairCandidates\": 2,\n    \"byVerdict\": {\n      \"complete\": 2,\n      \"incomplete\": 2\n    },\n    \"byPriority\": {\n      \"critical\": 4\n    }\n  },\n  \"repairPolicy\": {\n    \"repairableVerdicts\": [\n      \"incomplete\",\n      \"partial\"","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"translation-inputs\\phase-group-verdicts.json","time":{"start":1782387882266,"end":1782387882276}},"id":"prt_efe98b847001dPUd913cZjVFl7","sessionID":"ses_1016784edffe9LVyBWMwWC7FdS","messageID":"msg_efe989d4f001tUULqQVaaoaQPA"}}
