se-03-onboarding-login-profile\",\n+        \"sourceBehavior\": \"Profile.kt renders static profile content, placeholder card actions, and logout navigation only; it does not request runtime permissions, handle permission callbacks, or access protected platform APIs.\",\n+        \"targetBehavior\": \"No HarmonyOS permission request flow was added for the profile route because the inspected source profile screen has no permission or protected-API behavior to translate.\",\n+        \"verificationEvidence\": [\n+          \"Source review: D:/Kotlin2Cangjie/Foodike/app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/profile/Profile.kt contains composables for avatar, text, profile cards, and logout only; there are no permission launchers or protected platform API calls.\",\n+          \"Target review: entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/features/profile/profile_page.cj and entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj implement profile rendering and route actions without permission-kit calls.\"\n+        ],\n+        \"parityLevel\": \"not-applicable\",\n+        \"targetEndpoints\": [],\n+        \"tests\": [],\n+        \"notes\": \"Static-analysis permission tagging for Profile.kt was a false positive.\",\n+        \"deferredReason\": \"\",\n+        \"targetFallback\": \"\",\n+        \"risk\": \"\",\n+        \"futureCompletionPath\": \"\"\n+      }\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"featureId\": \"app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-profi-e492afed0c-004-observable-state-viewmodel-flow-livedata\",\n+      \"set\": {\n+        \"status\": \"implemented\",\n+        \"plannedPhase\": \"phase-03-onboarding-login-profile\",\n+        \"sourceBehavior\": \"Profile.kt keeps most profile content static, but it propagates UI actions through `ProfileViewModel.onEvent(ProfileEvent.PerformLogout)` and callback lambdas so logout navigation happens only after the view-model layer processes the event.\",\n+        \"targetBehavior\": \"The